## Testing Contract

- parse-feed accepts XML string or Reader
- Returns map with :id, :title, :updated, :entries keys
- Handles atom namespace transparently

## Boundaries

- Uses clojure.data.xml (not external parsers)
- No validation - pure parsing only
- Nil-safe: missing elements return nil

## Validation

```clojure
(require '[atom-validator.parser :as p])
(p/parse-feed "<feed>...</feed>")
;; => {:id "..." :title "..." :entries [...]}
```
